Summary: V shaped parallel to each other
divs: Sighting Details1. Outside looking at the stars and smoking a cigarette. 2. When i was looking at the stars it just appeared out of no where. 3. Thoght it was a flock of birds. 4. There were about six white objects parallel to each other. They were moving at a great rate of speed. They kind of glistened, thought it was the light from the city. But noticed no flapping of any wings. Travelling north from the south. It kinded glided in its direction and dissapered into the night sky. 5. Wow, not sure what i just saw. 6. Through the tree line.
